            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Thin self supporting yttrium foils (99.9% purity)of",
                "2 mg/cm2 thickness were prepared by proper rolling.",
                "Target foils and aluminium catcher foils from MERCK of",
                "1.5 mg/cm2 thickness were mounted on aluminum ring of",
                "12 mm inner and 22 mm outer diameter with 0.5 mm",
                "thickness. Each yttrium foil accompanies an aluminium",
                "catcher and such yttrium-aluminium combinations made a",
                "target stack."
              ]
